snippet.title: Marl DE Jigsaw [マールDEジクソー] Game Sample - PS2
snippet.description: Description later. However, this game plays quite a bit like other competitive jigsaw puzzle games (from Nippon Ichi or otherwise), but with LOADS of different artworks to unlock that show many different characters and places in the "Marl Kingdom" universe. If you have played "Pieces", for the SNES, you generally will know what to expect, gameplay-wise (as far as general functionality, not in game modes, unlockables, etc.).
